data.description: You will fall in love with living here! This all brick 1 level home offers an inground pool, great fenced backyard with 2 storage sheds, open kitchen with granite counters, versatile floorplan, hardwood floors, vinyl replacement windows, water heater & hvac 2 years & many more updates. The owner's suite can easily be converted back into two bedrooms to give this home 4 bedrooms if desired. Easy access to a public boat ramp, Surf Rider Restaurant, Bluewater Marina and public boat slips, enjoy fireworks from Downtown Hampton from your backyard, and interconnected streets allowing for space to bike or walk. No flood insurance is required. Make sure to view the 3D interactive tour to view more of this great home! Seller has FHA assumable mortgage @ 3.35% interest rate.
